	xmlns:skos="http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#"
	xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#">
	
	<owl:Ontology rdf:about="https://spec.edmcouncil.org/fibo/ontology/DER/DerivativesContracts/SwapsIndividuals/">
		<rdfs:label>Swaps Individuals Ontology</rdfs:label>
		<dct:abstract>This ontology specifies indiividuals that represent well-known swaps repositories and intermediaries. Related definitions for the corresponding legal entities can be found in the FBC Commercial Registration Authorities ontology. 
		
Note that this ontology is not intended to be exhaustive, but is designed for expansion as FIBO use cases or user requirements dictate.</dct:abstract>
